expression.original_otl:
| inputlookup tailaki_sensor_data_energy_latest_manual.csv
| sort  __pad_num, __well_num, ois_id
| fields __pad_num, __well_num, ois_id, avg_current, avg_voltage, adkuControlStationLoading, adkuControlStationFullPower, adkuControlStationActivePower, adkuControlStationPowerCoeff
| apply fillna strategy=const from avg_current avg_voltage adkuControlStationLoading adkuControlStationFullPower adkuControlStationActivePower adkuControlStationPowerCoeff 
| fields - fillna
